games.comment: Mark Ingram once again saw more carries (14) than Pierre Thomas (9).

Mark Ingram. The veteran running back was able to gash the beat-up Washington defense for most of the day. He finished with just 11 carries, due to the fact that the Saints were trailing most of the afternoon, but he put up a whopping 134 yards and a touchdown.
